ed="T" n="0893b16"/><persName key="A008828">釋澄心</persName>，姓朱氏，<placeName key="PL000000010400">東海</placeName>人也。厥父任<placeName key="PL000000024630">濟源</placeName>令。<lb
ed="T" n="0893b17"/><date key="j19921141997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15" notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14"><name>天寶</name>中</date>，安、史之亂遇害。<persName key="A008828">心</persName>穉齒隨母氏至<lb
ed="T" n="0893b18"/><placeName key="PL000000024671">河內</placeName>，貧極，母即從人。<persName key="A008828">心</persName>不樂隨嫁。<persName key="A008828">心</persName>之志<lb
ed="T" n="0893b19"/>氣不群，乃投應福寺<!--找不到此地--><persName key="A013912">智明法師</persName>求教勗，披<lb
ed="T" n="0893b20"/>削登戒。後雲遊鳥宿，務急參玄於<persName key="A009582">秀師</persName><ref type="person" target="#A009319">高<lb
ed="T" n="0893b21"/>足</ref>門下<ptr target="#n2084"/>，了其法要。乃觀諸方名跡，遂止<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡<lb
ed="T" n="0893b22"/>嶽</placeName>。請益之僧，摩肩駢足。時太守<persName key="A013913">吳憲忠</persName>請<lb
ed="T" n="0893b23"/><persName key="A008828">心</persName>入州治，謝而不行。再命棲于龍興寺<!--找不到此地-->，來<lb
ed="T" n="0893b24"/>問道者，丈室恒滿。<date key="j20143212014350" notAfter-iso="+0803-01-01" notBefore-iso="+0802-12-03"><name>貞元</name>十八年壬午十一月</date><lb
ed="T" n="0893b25"/>示滅，春秋七十六，以<date key="j20143472014347" when-iso="+0802-12-29">其月二十七日</date>入塔<lb
ed="T" n="0893b26"/>云。</p>
